      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently does not start, and there are major mechanical issues with the transmission and suspension that need immediate attention. The exterior has extensive rust, several large dents, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it will need to be towed from its current location.",
