    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid value for someone looking for a dependable driver that doesn't need to be perfect. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a few small dings typical of a car this age. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in top shape. It\u2019s an honest car with plenty of life left for a buyer who doesn't mind a bit of character.",
