    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to find a new home for this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it really shows in every little detail. If you're looking for something that feels brand new and has been totally pampered, this is definitely the one for you. I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out for a chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
