    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is mechanically superlative, with documented rod bearing service and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp gate engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Suspension bushings and dampers maintain original factory kinematics, delivering a pure, analog driving experience. A pristine, turn-key example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
