      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior paint retains its original deep luster with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and scent-free, with the original factory floor mats and untouched trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is flawless; it has been serviced exclusively by certified technicians, and a comprehensive binder of all service records is included. From the pristine undercarriage to the mirror-finish engine bay, every inch of this car reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. It performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory\u2014quiet, powerful, and perfectly balanced. This is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer.",
